    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THIS GAME</h2>Bor Dungeon is a fast paced action RPG mixing with platformer and simple puzzles. Smashing your way through dark dungeons defeating hordes of enemies and collecting loot, become the ultimate Bor!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/d66e1f539274a06ddd79489a65ff15c9.poster.avif?t=1692109461\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/d66e1f539274a06ddd79489a65ff15c9.webm?t=1692109461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/d66e1f539274a06ddd79489a65ff15c9.mp4?t=1692109461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play as third person Bor, collecting loot, gain unique skills and smashing huge Bosses!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2>▪️Action packed with physics: the game has interactive environment. You can jump on, smash, and examine anything in the level as your physics playground! <br>▪️Smooth and responsive movement and combat<br>▪️Cutesy design in enemies and environment<br>▪️Defeat big bosses to gain additional skills and unleash your full potential!<br>▪️No loot boxes, microtransactions or ANY additional purchases required- all content is available to unlock in game by playing.<br>▪️Each weapon type comes with different skill set.<br>▪️Challenging bosses with engaging combat!<br>Solo developed by Spikebor<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SMACK THINGS WITH YOUR HAMMER</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/da496efbefee1a9da28e1a022d042339.poster.avif?t=1692109461\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/da496efbefee1a9da28e1a022d042339.webm?t=1692109461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/da496efbefee1a9da28e1a022d042339.mp4?t=1692109461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >YOU CAN CLIMB ON BIG BOSS</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/c7ab1693271f9d238ad36fb7e9557f60.poster.avif?t=1692109461\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/c7ab1693271f9d238ad36fb7e9557f60.webm?t=1692109461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/c7ab1693271f9d238ad36fb7e9557f60.mp4?t=1692109461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CHALLENGING BOSS FIGHT!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/9b0367f6a765c5aaa1fc356cbfd9f9de.poster.avif?t=1692109461\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/9b0367f6a765c5aaa1fc356cbfd9f9de.webm?t=1692109461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/9b0367f6a765c5aaa1fc356cbfd9f9de.mp4?t=1692109461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAIN NEW SKILL EACH BOSS DEFEATED</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2388900/extras/db7c02b7645fa18e2fa50dd6a91d21f6.poster.avif?t=1692109461\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_ite